item.description: Cmd to build site /user/bin/hugo -s hugo new ../../docset/test.md Tools to generate pdf WKHTMLTOPDF Download theme(ananke) git submodule add https://github.com/budparr/gohugo-theme-ananke.git themes/ananke Download all hugo theme git clone –depth 1 –recursive https://github.com/gohugoio/hugoThemes.git themes add theme to config echo ‘theme = “ananke”’ >> config.toml Start Server(very important) hugo server -D
